snippet.title: Guild Saga: Vanished Worlds Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Guild Saga: Vanished Worlds launches in Early Access on October 10th on Steam. Aspiring adventurers can wishlist Guild Saga: Vanished Worlds today and get ready to lead your party to glory—or face the consequences of your choices. The fate of Aarde rests in your hands.

WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2184350/Guild_Saga_Vanished_Worlds/
